data.description: At first glance this home may seem modest in size, but upon closer inspection it becomes evident that it is much larger than it appears. Once you step inside you are greeted with spacious rooms and an abundance of living space.    This charming farmhouse style home offers 4 Bedroom 2.5 bathroom and is located in the Union Grove school district. It had been meticulously renovated with no expense spared! New flooring, new HVAC, new roof, new water heater, new bathrooms, Quartz countertops, tiled backsplash, new fixtures, new decks, etc. Enjoy your morning coffee on your oversized rocking chair front porch overlooking the beautiful 3.12 acres. The living room and dining room both boast a beautiful wood burning masonry fireplace making it warm and inviting while entertaining. The tranquil setting offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life while also conveniently located just minutes from the McDonough square, restaurants, shopping, I-75 and Highway 20. Call to schedule your tour today!
